## 1. Basic Information
- Model Name: 
- Business Unit: 
- Model Owner: 
- Risk/Compliance Reviewer: 
- Version: 
- Date: 

## 2. Use Case Description
- Problem AI solves
- Decision type: Advisory / Decision-Making / Autonomous
- Stakeholders affected

## 3. Context & Criticality Assessment
